<item>
            <title>[LU-3627] Incorrect NULL return value of qsd_init()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3627</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;qsd_init() might return NULL in some cases, which is not correct and&lt;br/&gt;
may make kernel crash. This patch fixes this problem.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
