                            <comment id="63369" author="lixi" created="Wed, 31 Jul 2013 14:24:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am so Sorry. I found I made a big mistake here. MGS failed to mount because qsd_init() return -EINVAL if the patch is applied.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am wondering why the autotest system did not stop me.Maybe it did not test the patch at all?&lt;/p&gt;

